parameters: 重さえおマップにも出す
メイズ外観イラストの削除

In the Golden Room, you can find a large number of treasure chests
that are more than just golden in color.

However, in order to eliminate adventurers who are after the treasures
in the Golden Room, guardians are patrolling.

The encounter rate with guardians is displayed in the bottom right
corner of the screen. It increases by 20% each time you progress.

The guardians are formidable enemies and cannot be escaped even with
smoke balls. Let's explore while avoiding encounters.

Would you like to proceed to the next step?

After finishing exploring the surroundings, I looked up and found
something faintly shining in front of me, so I thought it was time to
turn back.
Taking the green orb in hand, I pondered for a moment---

---Huh!? Could it be that if I take this, the ceiling will come crashing
down?! In an instant, such thoughts crossed my mind, and I looked
around nervously.

However, there doesn't seem to be any noticeable change. What could
this possibly be? For now, \N[1] decided to take the orb back home.
